data.description: This 4-bedroom/2.5-bathroom home is located in the Wolf Creek neighborhood in Broken Arrow, and is ready for its new owners. The home has two living areas on the main level, one with a fireplace and the other that could accommodate a table for a large gathering. The kitchen has ample storage and counter space with updated stainless-steel appliances. The spacious, primary bedroom is located on the main level with a private bath, step-in shower, soaking tub, and walk-in closet. The additional 3 bedrooms can be found nestled upstairs with a full bath.
